<article class="border-l-4 border-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] pl-6">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">July 12, 2026</h2>
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">Conversion pass on the homepage to route breeder intent into the free trial and set price expectations earlier.</p>
  <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
    <li><strong>Fixed breeder CTA routing:</strong> the "For Breeders" card CTA and the final segmented CTA now point to the register-with-trial URL instead of the login page. First-time visitors were being sent to a login screen with no account, a dead end. Both now read "Start your 14-day free trial."</li>
    <li><strong>Hero trial hook:</strong> added a breeder-specific sub-line under the ecosystem positioning: "14-day free trial, plans from $29/mo, and never a percentage of your sales." Surfaces the trial and price above the fold without changing the three-audience CTA layout.</li>
  </ul>
</article>
